<div class="title">Paranoia and Hallucinations</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Phantom&Exact=1">Phantom</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Phantom. "Paranoia and Hallucinations: An Experience with Caffeine (exp25018)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 25, 2007. erowid.org/exp/25018</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

<!-- DoseChart -->
